title: Royal baby photo: Live updates - CNN
description: View the latest news and breaking news today for U.S., world, weather, entertainment, politics and health at CNN.com.
content:
What's happening: The world finally has its first glimpse of Prince Harry and Meghan's newborn.

All in a name? Harry, the Duke of Sussex, and Meghan have revealed their son will be called Archie Harrison Mountbatten-Windsor.

What we know: The newborn arrived at 5:26 a.m. (12:26 a.m. ET), weighing 7 pounds, 3 ounces on Monday. He is the seventh-in-line to the British throne.
